{
  "video_id": "EZKDkSY1GBM",
  "title": "A playful solution to the housing crisis | Sarah Murray",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Ivana Korom Reviewer: Camille Mart√≠nez"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13507.0,
      "end_time": 14920.0,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14944.0,
      "end_time": 16158.0,
      "text": "My name&#39;s Sarah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 17870.0,
      "end_time": 19926.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve been priced out of the housing market."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21809.0,
      "end_time": 22992.0,
      "text": "In fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24395.0,
      "end_time": 27967.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m one of the majority of my generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27991.0,
      "end_time": 30790.0,
      "text": "who can&#39;t afford a home."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31228.0,
      "end_time": 36227.0,
      "text": "And in 2017, home ownership amongst young Australians"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36251.0,
      "end_time": 41175.0,
      "text": "has fallen to the lowest level in recorded history."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42601.0,
      "end_time": 46141.0,
      "text": "So, foolishly or otherwise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46165.0,
      "end_time": 48850.0,
      "text": "I decided to build my own home."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49585.0,
      "end_time": 52116.0,
      "text": "But the prognosis wasn&#39;t good there, either."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53690.0,
      "end_time": 56203.0,
      "text": "Architects cater for the one percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56227.0,
      "end_time": 57806.0,
      "text": "builders are scarce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57831.0,
      "end_time": 61378.0,
      "text": "so service is inconsistent and prices are high."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62325.0,
      "end_time": 66530.0,
      "text": "The single biggest investment in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66770.0,
      "end_time": 69810.0,
      "text": "and I was amazed how little self-determination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70704.0,
      "end_time": 71863.0,
      "text": "choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72442.0,
      "end_time": 74886.0,
      "text": "and, ultimately, control I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76530.0,
      "end_time": 81780.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s more, I was doubly surprised at how vulnerable this made me feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 82560.0,
      "end_time": 85255.0,
      "text": "Frankly, I felt trapped."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87923.0,
      "end_time": 92158.0,
      "text": "So, I reflected on this for quite some time."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93310.0,
      "end_time": 94594.0,
      "text": "And I realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94618.0,
      "end_time": 100330.0,
      "text": "what I wanted was democratized design and construction."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 101975.0,
      "end_time": 106286.0,
      "text": "And that led to me asking one very simple question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 107452.0,
      "end_time": 109919.0,
      "text": "What is building a house?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 111332.0,
      "end_time": 112482.0,
      "text": "What is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 112934.0,
      "end_time": 117109.0,
      "text": "Well, it turns out that building a house"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 117133.0,
      "end_time": 122616.0,
      "text": "is making a series of decisions, some with physical consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 122641.0,
      "end_time": 126920.0,
      "text": "within a defined set of parameters."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 126950.0,
      "end_time": 130728.0,
      "text": "Now, having worked in software applications for some time now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 130752.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132759.00000000003,
      "text": "this all sounded very familiar to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 133696.0,
      "end_time": 137450.0,
      "text": "I also couldn&#39;t understand why we build on-site."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 138442.0,
      "end_time": 143296.0,
      "text": "No other major assembly in our lives is constructed like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 143944.0,
      "end_time": 146690.0,
      "text": "Your car doesn&#39;t come to you in pieces"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 146714.0,
      "end_time": 149165.0,
      "text": "with an extra 10 percent just in case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 149189.0,
      "end_time": 152422.0,
      "text": "to be assembled at the mercy of the elements."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 152849.0,
      "end_time": 154600.0,
      "text": "So why should your house?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 156460.0,
      "end_time": 159301.0,
      "text": "So I built a computer game."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 160532.0,
      "end_time": 163960.0,
      "text": "A game that allows you to design your home"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 163984.0,
      "end_time": 165783.0,
      "text": "and have it delivered to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 165807.0,
      "end_time": 169450.0,
      "text": "A game that puts the home builder"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 169474.0,
      "end_time": 174620.0,
      "text": "back at the center of the largest purchase in their life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 175266.0,
      "end_time": 179646.0,
      "text": "elevating them from spectator to player."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 180927.0,
      "end_time": 185376.0,
      "text": "A game with full visibility of the costs and environmental impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 185400.0,
      "end_time": 187668.0,
      "text": "of each new attribute you add."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 188466.0,
      "end_time": 193370.0,
      "text": "Using modular components, players select items from their library"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 193610.0,
      "end_time": 195128.0,
      "text": "and drag them into their world."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 196530.0,
      "end_time": 202222.0,
      "text": "Each item, be it a wall, a solar battery or even an armchair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 202246.0,
      "end_time": 206719.0,
      "text": "contains all of the information for the system to calculate costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 206743.0,
      "end_time": 208641.0,
      "text": "environmental impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 208665.0,
      "end_time": 211578.0,
      "text": "and even a happiness tally for the player."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 213371.0,
      "end_time": 217478.0,
      "text": "Eighty-three percent of home builders said that next to cost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 217502.0,
      "end_time": 222910.0,
      "text": "environmentally friendly features were the most important things to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 222553.0,
      "end_time": 226619.0,
      "text": "So out of the gate, homes are integrated with solar systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 227276.0,
      "end_time": 229265.0,
      "text": "Born green."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 230321.0,
      "end_time": 234712.0,
      "text": "Sustainable housing is often associated with wealth and affluence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 234736.0,
      "end_time": 236378.0,
      "text": "but that shouldn&#39;t be the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 236720.0,
      "end_time": 241228.0,
      "text": "In fact, truly sustainable housing should be available to everyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 241253.0,
      "end_time": 243316.0,
      "text": "and affordable for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 244563.0,
      "end_time": 251337.0,
      "text": "So, I had found a way to get the control back that I was craving"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 252290.0,
      "end_time": 254162.0,
      "text": "and give it to others."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 255173.0,
      "end_time": 256863.0,
      "text": "But something was still bugging me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 256887.0,
      "end_time": 258902.0,
      "text": "something was still keeping me up at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 261380.0,
      "end_time": 262905.0,
      "text": "What about those people"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 263783.0,
      "end_time": 268591.0,
      "text": "who have genuinely no control over where they live?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 269704.0,
      "end_time": 273848.0,
      "text": "Every hour -- in the space of your intermission --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 273872.0,
      "end_time": 278152.0,
      "text": "4,000 new homes are needed in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 278506.0,
      "end_time": 280361.0,
      "text": "Wrap your head around that number."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 281585.0,
      "end_time": 288385.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an astonishing 35 million homes globally, every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 289641.0,
      "end_time": 291387.0,
      "text": "And in Australia alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 291411.0,
      "end_time": 295902.0,
      "text": "we have a shortfall of 250,000 dwellings."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 296768.0,
      "end_time": 299933.0,
      "text": "And in addition to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 299958.0,
      "end_time": 305799.0,
      "text": "we have 190,000 families on the assisted-housing wait list;"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 306481.0,
      "end_time": 309847.0,
      "text": "families in need of a home."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 311615.0,
      "end_time": 314687.0,
      "text": "Between now and 2050,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 314711.0,
      "end_time": 321600.0,
      "text": "when the global population is set to move from today&#39;s 7.6 billion"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 321624.0,
      "end_time": 326710.0,
      "text": "to tomorrow&#39;s 9.8 billion people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 326734.0,
      "end_time": 329996.0,
      "text": "hundreds of millions of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 330200.0,
      "end_time": 334977.0,
      "text": "will experience security, health and safety issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 337127.0,
      "end_time": 341681.0,
      "text": "Imagine if you can not feeling secure in your home --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 342626.0,
      "end_time": 345870.0,
      "text": "not from crime, not from theft,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 346149.0,
      "end_time": 349117.0,
      "text": "but from the fact that the building you&#39;re in --"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 349141.0,
      "end_time": 350347.0,
      "text": "the building you&#39;re in --"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 350371.0,
      "end_time": 352304.0,
      "text": "might not be structurally sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 353268.0,
      "end_time": 355871.0,
      "text": "or built from nontoxic components"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 355895.0,
      "end_time": 358628.0,
      "text": "or meet local natural disaster standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 360926.0,
      "end_time": 362823.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the 21st century."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 363760.0,
      "end_time": 366299.0,
      "text": "And this just isn&#39;t good enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 369395.0,
      "end_time": 371667.0,
      "text": "What if -- what if --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 373167.0,
      "end_time": 378695.0,
      "text": "we could restore control and dignity to those individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 378720.0,
      "end_time": 382750.0,
      "text": "by giving them a home, but not just any home:"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 383165.0,
      "end_time": 384315.0,
      "text": "their home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 384823.0,
      "end_time": 386623.0,
      "text": "and a home of their design."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 387756.0,
      "end_time": 391854.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re currently adapting our game so that when a player builds a home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 391879.0,
      "end_time": 394852.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re contributing to a home for someone in need."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 395791.0,
      "end_time": 398690.0,
      "text": "And I know this sounds like a lofty goal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 398930.0,
      "end_time": 400227.0,
      "text": "and it is ridiculously ambitious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 400839.0,
      "end_time": 403617.0,
      "text": "but today, our current operating model"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 403641.0,
      "end_time": 406251.0,
      "text": "operates at a ten-to-one ratio."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 406691.0,
      "end_time": 409800.0,
      "text": "So for every 10 homes we build,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 409320.0,
      "end_time": 412264.0,
      "text": "we can build a home for someone in need."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 412701.0,
      "end_time": 417675.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 418220.0,
      "end_time": 421760.0,
      "text": "This is made possible because today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 421784.0,
      "end_time": 424563.0,
      "text": "with design for manufacture and assembly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 425538.0,
      "end_time": 430290.0,
      "text": "which uses light gauge steel frame construction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 430530.0,
      "end_time": 432450.0,
      "text": "shipped and assembled on-site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 432474.0,
      "end_time": 435394.0,
      "text": "we can decrease construction costs by 20 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 435418.0,
      "end_time": 438472.0,
      "text": "and environmental waste by 15 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 438496.0,
      "end_time": 440757.0,
      "text": "saving time, money"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 440781.0,
      "end_time": 443988.0,
      "text": "and keeping tons of waste out of landfills."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 444586.0,
      "end_time": 447967.0,
      "text": "The power in modular construction"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 447991.0,
      "end_time": 452825.0,
      "text": "is that you can build year-round with confidence in your costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 453902.0,
      "end_time": 455609.0,
      "text": "in your quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 455633.0,
      "end_time": 458236.0,
      "text": "and in your delivery date, in your build date."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 460779.0,
      "text": "Now, wouldn&#39;t that be crazy? Wouldn&#39;t that be great?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 461807.0,
      "end_time": 463770.0,
      "text": "But --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 465189.0,
      "end_time": 467434.0,
      "text": "that doesn&#39;t get me to my goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 467458.0,
      "end_time": 471184.0,
      "text": "My goal is one-for-one."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 472863.0,
      "end_time": 475300.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve been traveling the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 475324.0,
      "end_time": 478649.0,
      "text": "looking at different alternatives of construction 3-D printing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 478673.0,
      "end_time": 482331.0,
      "text": "trying to find technology that will help me deliver on my ambition."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 482919.0,
      "end_time": 487258.0,
      "text": "3-D printing is so exciting and so promising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 487283.0,
      "end_time": 491577.0,
      "text": "offering a 40 percent reduction in cost and near zero waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 492546.0,
      "end_time": 494252.0,
      "text": "And this is just to name a few,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 494276.0,
      "end_time": 497748.0,
      "text": "but some of the really exciting innovations happening all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 497772.0,
      "end_time": 500784.0,
      "text": "are happening in Italy, France, Dubai and Australia."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 501101.0,
      "end_time": 505453.0,
      "text": "And they use robotic arms to print everything from solid stone"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 505477.0,
      "end_time": 506907.0,
      "text": "to concrete, to wax."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 506932.0,
      "end_time": 510849.0,
      "text": "In Italy, they have developed a technique using sorel cement."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 511182.0,
      "end_time": 515556.0,
      "text": "Sorel cement was originally invented in 1867,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 516850.0,
      "end_time": 522371.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s the beautiful chemical marriage of magnesium oxide and local sand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 522395.0,
      "end_time": 526163.0,
      "text": "which they can now use to print solid stone walls."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 526601.0,
      "end_time": 527783.0,
      "text": "And in France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 527807.0,
      "end_time": 531362.0,
      "text": "they have a regulator-approved although still experimental process"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 531386.0,
      "end_time": 534949.0,
      "text": "where they print two parallel tracks of foam insulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 534974.0,
      "end_time": 538570.0,
      "text": "and pour concrete in the middle to create solid stone."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 539610.0,
      "end_time": 544942.0,
      "text": "And in Dubai, sitting at the foot of those two glorious Emirates Towers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 544966.0,
      "end_time": 547910.0,
      "text": "is a vision of the future in the middle of the desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 547934.0,
      "end_time": 551512.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve got their experimental office of the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 551537.0,
      "end_time": 554918.0,
      "text": "which is constructed using 3-D printed concrete"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 554942.0,
      "end_time": 556292.0,
      "text": "which was printed in China"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 556316.0,
      "end_time": 558940.0,
      "text": "and shipped and assembled on location in Dubai."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 559530.0,
      "end_time": 560805.0,
      "text": "And not to be outdone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 560830.0,
      "end_time": 564433.0,
      "text": "in Australia, we&#39;ve pioneered an amazing technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 564457.0,
      "end_time": 566974.0,
      "text": "that allows you to print wax molds"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 566998.0,
      "end_time": 569498.0,
      "text": "and pour concrete over the top of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 569522.0,
      "end_time": 575188.0,
      "text": "allowing you to create really intricately beautiful and cost-effective facades"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 575212.0,
      "end_time": 576527.0,
      "text": "that you can see in person"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 576551.0,
      "end_time": 578966.0,
      "text": "the next time you travel the London Underground."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 578990.0,
      "end_time": 581998.0,
      "text": "But all of these things are tools --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 582488.0,
      "end_time": 584789.0,
      "text": "hammer of tomorrow, if you like."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 584813.0,
      "end_time": 587845.0,
      "text": "And the one common thread that connects all these things"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 587869.0,
      "end_time": 590281.0,
      "text": "is computer-aided design."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 590305.0,
      "end_time": 595780.0,
      "text": "We will need models to build using these techniques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 595434.0,
      "end_time": 600110.0,
      "text": "models like the ones being developed by players in our game."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 602545.0,
      "end_time": 606570.0,
      "text": "I want to put every person that wants one"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 606595.0,
      "end_time": 608779.0,
      "text": "in a home of their own design."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 609761.0,
      "end_time": 612690.0,
      "text": "And there are many more applications still."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 612476.0,
      "end_time": 617213.0,
      "text": "We could usher in an entirely new empowered experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 617237.0,
      "end_time": 620380.0,
      "text": "of special needs or aged-care accommodation."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 620737.0,
      "end_time": 623307.0,
      "text": "And we could provide rapid, on-site assistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 623331.0,
      "end_time": 625464.0,
      "text": "in emergency housing situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 626371.0,
      "end_time": 628855.0,
      "text": "In the words of one of my players,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 628879.0,
      "end_time": 631814.0,
      "text": "\"I want to take matters into my own hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 631838.0,
      "end_time": 634940.0,
      "text": "and live by example.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 635371.0,
      "end_time": 636521.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 636546.0,
      "end_time": 639559.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}